                <header class="news-detail-header">
                    <h1 class="news-detail-title font-bold">Registrations for Free Fire India Championship 2022 Spring opening soon!</h1>
                    <p class="news-detail-time publish-time" data-time="Feb. 2, 2022, 6 p.m.">
                        02/02</p>
                </header>
                <section class="news-content">
                    <img class="news-cover-img lazy-img"
                         src="https://dl.dir.freefiremobile.com/common/web_event/esports_static/lazybg.png"
                         data-src="https://dl.dir.freefiremobile.com/common/Local/IND/config/FFIC2022SpringAnnouncement_492.jpg" alt="Registrations for Free Fire India Championship 2022 Spring opening soon!"
                         title="FFIC 2022 Spring Announcement, #WhereChampionsAreMade, #FFIC2022Spring, FFIC 2022 Spring Registration Process"/>
                    <br>
                    
                    <p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="color:#ffffff">The next stop on our esports roadmap for 2022 is the flagship tournament of the year. We are pleased to announce the </span><span style="color:#e67e22"><strong>Free Fire India Championship 2022 Spring!</strong></span><span style="color:#ffffff"> This time, it&rsquo;s bigger and better than ever before. This trophy calls to the best of the best, and the worthy will walk away with the lion&rsquo;s share of the mammoth </span><span style="color:#f1c40f"><strong>INR 1 Crore Prize pool</strong></span><span style="color:#ffffff">. But what&rsquo;s more important is eternal glory and a chance to represent India at the global stage.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p><span style="color:#ffffff">The extravaganza begins on <strong>The match starts </strong>. The contestants will begin with the</span><span style="color:#2ecc71"><strong> FFC Mode Open Qualifiers</strong></span><span style="color:#ffffff"> that will take place in-game. The registrations for the same will be live from </span><span style="color:#f1c40f"><strong>Each tournament starts at present year </strong></span><span style="color:#ffffff"><strong>. </strong>Let&rsquo;s take you through the registration process.&nbsp;</span></p>
