<p><span style="color:#e74c3c"><strong>Here is a step-by-step guide on how to register:</strong></span></p>

<p><span style="color:#2ecc71"><strong>Step 1:</strong></span><span style="color:#ffffff"><strong> </strong>To start the registration process, login into your game account which locate in above .&nbsp;</span></p>

<p><span style="color:#2ecc71"><strong>Step 2:</strong></span><span style="color:#ffffff"><strong> </strong>The FFIC 2022 Spring banner will appear on your window. Here you will find all the necessary details including scheduling, scoring and progression. </span><span style="color:#e67e22"><em>(Note: If you do not meet the eligibility criteria to participate, this section will remain locked)</em></span></p>

<p><span style="color:#2ecc71"><strong>Step 3: </strong></span><span style="color:#ffffff">Now, find the squad button at the top right corner. Tap on it to create or join your FFIC squad.</span></p>

<p><span style="color:#2ecc71"><strong>Step 4:</strong></span><span style="color:#ffffff"> Enter team details-name, contact details, region, avatar and banner.</span></p>

<p><span style="color:#2ecc71"><strong>Step 5:</strong></span><span style="color:#ffffff"><strong> </strong>To play in FFC Mode, invite the registered squad members via the invite friends options in the </span><span style="color:#f1c40f"><em>Free Fire India Championship&nbsp;2022 Spring</em></span><span style="color:#ffffff"> lobby.</span></p>

<p><span style="color:#ffffff">The match day for FFC Mode Qualifiers is </span><span style="color:#f1c40f"><strong>from 3 PM to 8 PM IST</strong></span><span style="color:#ffffff">. Players have to complete a minimum of 5 matches in order to qualify for the next stage. Players that meet the eligibility criteria have a five day window to assemble their squad and register for the tournament.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img src="tour.jpg" style="height:624px; width:624px" />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#ffffff">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p><span style="color:#e74c3c"><strong>You must complete the following eligibility criteria to participate:</strong></span></p>

<ul>
	<li style="list-style-type:disc">
	<p><strong><span style="color:#ffffff">1. The minimum rank for registrations for all team members must be Diamond I and Level 40&nbsp;with a rank point of 2538 throughout the entire period of the FFIC 2022 Spring FFC&nbsp;Qualifiers.</span></strong></p>
	</li>
	<li style="list-style-type:disc">
	<p><strong><span style="color:#ffffff">2. Top 42 shortlisted teams will advance to FFIC 2022 Spring Closed Qualifiers.</span></strong></p>
	</li>
	<li style="list-style-type:disc">
	<p><strong><span style="color:#ffffff">3. A total of 10 tickets will be given to each team for matchmaking. The best&nbsp;5 scores from 10 rounds will be used to determine the team&#39;s final ranking.</span></strong></p>
	</li>
	<li style="list-style-type:disc">
	<p><strong><span style="color:#ffffff">4. To change your team roster, you will first need to disband the team and the teams that have used at least 1 ticket will not be allowed to disband.</span></strong></p>
	</li>
	<li style="list-style-type:disc">
	<p><strong><span style="color:#ffffff">5. Players are not allowed to participate in multiple teams for FFC Mode (either as a player or substitute or with multiple accounts).</span></strong></p>
	</li>
	<li style="list-style-type:disc">
	<p><strong><span style="color:#ffffff">6. All players must be citizens of India or Nepal.</span></strong></p>
	</li>
	<li style="list-style-type:disc">
	<p><strong><span style="color:#ffffff">7. Team are required to have a minimum of 5 players and maximum of 6 players.</span></strong></p>
	</li>
	<li style="list-style-type:disc">
	<p><strong><span style="color:#ffffff">8. All players have to 16 years of age or older in 2022.</span></strong></p>
	</li>
	<li style="list-style-type:disc">
	<p><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/q3kymC0N0k8X0gT52IVV2LSixDK5k2dnSGZE6UuqsjBZiU6r0osIGuTCW3TBpBDq1KPvNvjE0N3xytpelY4X6FMEu51v_nW8wuCLXFD71cZHUy9mptTW6YNvGIhqzzGfvs3YxyLa" style="height:624px; width:624px" />&nbsp;</span></p>
	</li>
</ul>

<p><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p>

<p><span style="color:#ffffff">Ignite your inner fire and seize the glory! </span><span style="color:#3498db"><em>Get ready to register for the biggest flagship tournament of 2022!&nbsp;</em></span></p>

